{"1209990": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "烈山海一(BMS1)", "steam_appid": 1209990, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [1493330], "detailed_description": "<strong>《烈山海》是一款以中国神话为背景的RPG游戏，玩家在游戏中将扮演一位身负奇异命运的穿越者，在机缘巧合之下来到山海境，与神农、夸父、精卫等经典神话人物相遇，一边改写他们的命运，一边完成自己的冒险…… 游戏尚在完善期，您有任何的意见或不满，都欢迎进入到我们的游戏QQ群704839701，感恩一路有你！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209990/extras/09b2a38b2f12184f6ea708778edb2036.avif?t=1708234817\" width=800 height=320 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>【故事背景】</li></ul>       山海境，乃神、妖、人共生共存之世界。彼时天界至高者天帝，与地界叛乱者刑天，刀兵不断，战火焚燃，只为争夺山海境统治之权。最终，刑天兵败，被封印于昆仑山下。然而天帝与刑天，终究谁也杀不死谁。刑天余众四处奔走，寻求解救之法；天帝为镇压刑天，无法离开昆仑山，也导致天界神权腐化，四方诸侯异心。 此时，一则“天命之人，山海共主”的预言流传开来，山海能人异士或是自号、或是寻找、或是当成无稽之谈，纷纷扰扰，山海局势更加动荡混乱。天命之人，到底是谁；他又是否真的是，山海共主呢？<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>【游戏特色】</li></ul>       致敬中国传统文化，独特的剪影美术风格，深入人心的剧情。卷入青丘地区的阴谋动荡，纷争不断的大地，注定终有一方胜、一方败。而玩家在其中的决定，将影响一条小道乃至整个青丘区域的安危。最终到底，何处歌舞升平，何方生灵涂炭呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209990/extras/be6037f1f8844c945d4ba52a65588c18.poster.avif?t=1708234817\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209990/extras/be6037f1f8844c945d4ba52a65588c18.webm?t=1708234817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209990/extras/be6037f1f8844c945d4ba52a65588c18.mp4?t=1708234817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>      角色和怪物以《山海经》为原型所创作，极大满足中国神话爱好者的需求。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209990/extras/c2dcd514c6a5fc1bf9a3e4d38af62127.poster.avif?t=1708234817\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209990/extras/c2dcd514c6a5fc1bf9a3e4d38af62127.webm?t=1708234817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209990/extras/c2dcd514c6a5fc1bf9a3e4d38af62127.mp4?t=1708234817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>      丰富的玩法和成长系统。可以升级成长、击败强敌、获得秘籍、学习各类招式，以简单的鼠标左右键组合，打出或单点突破、或范围杀伤、或切入切出的攻击组合。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209990/extras/61dc7efd6be82e4a1e76a0ce8d576dfd.poster.avif?t=1708234817\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209990/extras/61dc7efd6be82e4a1e76a0ce8d576dfd.webm?t=1708234817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209990/extras/61dc7efd6be82e4a1e76a0ce8d576dfd.mp4?t=1708234817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>      好玩的小游戏和奇遇任务。参与青丘声色犬马的生活，偶遇精卫解救水底生物，对话神农、夸父，完成小游戏获得报酬。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209990/extras/42e0bb3f06aed841947c86e7ccf8b5bc.poster.avif?t=1708234817\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209990/extras/42e0bb3f06aed841947c86e7ccf8b5bc.webm?t=1708234817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1209990/extras/42e0bb3f06aed841947c86e7ccf8b5bc.mp4?t=1708234817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>", "about_the_game": "<strong>《烈山海》是一款以中国神话为背景的RPG游戏，玩家在游戏中将扮演一位身负奇异命运的穿越者，在机缘巧合之下来到山海境，与神农、夸父、精卫等经典神话人物相遇，一边改写他们的命运，一边完成自己的冒险…… 游戏尚在完善期，您有任何的意见或不满，都欢迎进入到我们的游戏QQ群704839701，感恩一路有你！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akama